      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is literally impossible to reach and i hate being stuck in the middle of the night if my sugar drops. it feels way safer to just skip it for one night since my levels are normal now. if i dont take it, what's the actual huge risk compared to just having a low from too much insulin? it's just one night of basal, it shouldn't make a massive difference right?",
